snippet.title: Virtua Tennis 2009 - Launch Trailer!
snippet.description:
ESRB Rating: EVERYONE

Virtua Tennis 2009 is on its way to retailers across the US! To celebrate, we've got another new trailer for you guys to enjoy - and some cool Virtua Tennis merch on our blogs, too:

http://blogs.sega.com/usa/2009/06/09/virtua-tennis-2009-ships-today-in-other-news-we-have-awesome-vt-swag/
